uation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">end</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code> to determine the beginning and the total number of lines</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Expected Behavior</h3>\n<p>When launching this application you will see:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A window with a background of bright pink and a black bar in the middle</li>\n<li>Text that has been loaded in and is revealed on an interval using a typewriter effect</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Instructions for use:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Running the application will start the animation of the text being revealed</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Other classes used in this file</h3>\n<p>This Example uses no other classes.</p>\n","type":"folder"}}],"fetch":[]}